verbose_text: Our results showed that mice immunized with pVAX-TgCDPK2 could elicit special humoral and cellular responses, with higher levels of IgG antibody, and increased levels of Th1-type cytokines IFN-gamma, IL-12 (p70), and CD3 + CD4 + CD8 - and CD3 + CD8 + CD4 - T cells, and had a prolonged survival time (14.0 +/- 2.32 days) compared to control mice.
